{"tid":885261,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"WhatsApp咁撚鳩屎點解你地仲要同佢整sticker?","createTime":"2018-11-01T07:59:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-01T08:09:00.000Z","uid":76329,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"bce45140167bbdf37d655a186087d065091d1d63","tid":885261,"uid":76329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T07:59:40.000Z","msg":"Whatsapp比豬閪伯格買起左之後已經變左垃圾<br />\n好地地有個telegram比你地任玩gif用sticker<br />\n而家Whatsapp出返個出黎又狗衝，仲要撚狗咁得官方sticker先用得<br />\n你班仆街為左個咁嘅新function又出破解又寫app，變相就好似支持佢咁<br />\n你老味，係想玩sticker班人就一早去撚左用tg啦<br />\n洗撚等你個Whtasapp咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又要屌佢黎緊出廣告又係到話佢function抄tg<br />\n轉個撚頭出個sticker功能好似發玩新大陸咁爆幾個post<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f7c4dd0aad39ffe58415d8974d31579c8b2489a","tid":885261,"uid":76329,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T08:01:50.000Z","msg":"真係唔撚明<br />\n又要做雞又要攞貞節牌坊"},{"pid":"afc7a23f70bd11efe75f8b88d2b8d3a922bfb02f","tid":885261,"uid":176063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T08:03:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fec83b90dd7f1f811c4f3814d80761bca33a7903","tid":885261,"uid":76329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T08:08:47.000Z","msg":"android一樣有人用root"},{"pid":"629f9a7d7fe60afc759ac2c9805323f3a39a6d42","tid":885261,"uid":76329,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"afc7a23f70bd11efe75f8b88d2b8d3a922bfb02f","tid":885261,"uid":176063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T08:03:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T08:09:00.000Z","msg":"android一樣有人用root"}]}